      "x": -100,
      "y": 700,
      "width": 1380,
      "height": 130,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "auth-flow-title",
      "x": -80,
      "y": 710,
      "width": 150,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "Auth Flow (OAuth)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "auth-flow-detail",
      "x": -80,
      "y": 740,
      "width": 1340,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "1. Browser → /auth/github/authorize → 302 to GitHub OAuth\n2. GitHub → /auth/github/callback?code=X → exchanges code for token\n3. Redirect to frontend /?session_token={github_token}&login={user}\n4. Frontend stores token in sessionStorage → sends as Bearer on /api/* calls\n5. API validates token via GET /user (cached 5min by SHA-256 hash) + checks org membership",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

